Task 1. Website: Flipkart

1. Login popup opens automatically :
When I opened the Flipkart homepage, the login popup came automatically.
Why I think it is a defect: Sometimes I just want to see products, but the popup comes first and interrupts me.


2. Search suggestions come a little late :
When I typed in the search box, the suggestions took some time to appear.
Why I think it is a defect: It makes searching slower and is not a smooth experience.


3. Homepage banners load slowly:
Some images and banners took a few seconds to load.
Why I think it is a defect: Users have to wait to see offers,so it gives a poor user experience.